data.description: Spacious 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom condominium located in a desirable community. This home features vaulted ceilings, a walkout balcony and various updates throughout. All appliances are less than 5 years old and fresh granite countertops and backsplash has been updated in both kitchen and bathroom. HOA includes a luxurious clubhouse, gym, pool and sauna all on site for your convenience. Come see what this beautiful condo at Maple Leaf has to offer.
